headline: ADP Workforce Now® Named a Leader in Human Capital Management 2025 Evaluation by Independent Research Firm
summary: ADP Workforce Now® has been recognized as a Leader in The Forrester Wave™: Human Capital Management Solutions, Q4 2025 evaluation. ADP Workforce Now received the highest scores possible in 17 criteria within the Current Offering and Strategy categories. ADP Workforce Now was chosen as a Leader after being evaluated alongside eleven other vendors in this comprehensive review.
